Class Test_for_String_printer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.dalayach.Print_tools.Test_for_String_printer

  • public class Test_for_String_printer
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests String_printer functions for their ability to provide correctly formatted strings, account for new lines accurately, and to ensure that the shortened version of each print function works as expected.
